-- Ancient Olympia Museum Robbed of Antiquities Early Today, Greek Police Say
-- B y   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 2012-02-17T08:40:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-17/ancient-olympia-museum-robbed-of-antiquities-early-today-greek-police-say.html
Greek police said the museum at the
site of ancient Olympia was robbed early today.  A police spokeswoman, who declined to be named, said the
heist was carried out by two perpetrators, who removed a number
of ancient copper items.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eleni Chrepa in Athens at 
